
.row
  .columns.large-7
    %h3
      Searching for:
      %q #{params[:q]}
    %p (Pro-tip: Use <strong>*</strong> to tell Sphinx to use wildcards so you can search partial strings instead of whole words)
.row
  .columns.large-10
    = render :partial => 'results', :collection => @results
.row
  .columns.large-8
  .columns.large-4
    = will_paginate @results